 www.iteris.com
 
      Iteris, Inc. is a leading provider of advanced information, software and sensor technologies that improve the efficiency and safety of surface transportation.
     Iteris manufactures and sells its Vantage video detection system for traffic control applications at intersections worldwide, giving traffic managers tools to mitigate traffic congestion by modifying traffic signal timing or detecting incidents.  Vantage also offers data collection software solutions for highway management.
     The Transportation Systems division applies advanced engineering, experience and imagination to create superior Intelligent Transportation Systems (ITS).
  


 



