Companies
Iteris, Inc.
 






Iteris is leading the world in applied informatics—turning big data into smart insights for transportation and agriculture. By using machine learning to extract the information engineers and scientists need to solve complex problems, we’re making our roads safer and our farms smarter. Building better communities today means we’re creating a better world tomorrow. Iteris provides products, services, and solutions to improve the efficiency of farms and roads in 40 countries, to help communities throughout the world optimize crop yield and keep their roads safe.

